track_notes: Track from Wägitalersee Parking up to Zindlenspitz

A route which leads from Zindlenspitz down to the Wägitalersee and can be used both for ascent and for descent. Note that since HB/GL-033, HB/GL-031 and HB/SZ-034 are in such close proximity to each other, they can all be done in a single day. For possible routes between the summits, please check the tracks on HB/GL-033 and HB/GL-031.

This route is fairly easy and leads over gentle, rocky paths from the summit all the way down to the lake. Note that if you want to ascend that parking spaces at the lake are limited and the lake is a popular fishing and tourist location. Arrive early if you want to secure a parking spot!
